eat up the priests, who had planned to spray insecticide around the area, the BBC reported. They also vandalized the nearby town council building, setting fire to it after burning the priests&#8217; car.<\/p>\n<p>Guinea, one of the three West African countries worst affected by the Ebola outbreak, has lost nearly 2,000 people to the disease. The nation&#8217;s schools reopened earlier this week following a five-month break, soon after the U.N. said the number of cases nationwide had fallen to its lowest weekly total since August.<\/p>\n<p>[<em><a href=\"http:\/\/www.bbc.com\/news\/world-africa-30900917\" target=\"_blank\">BBC<\/a><\/em>]<\/p>\n<aside class=\"right-rail-module rr-share\" data-name=\"rr-share\"><span class=\"social-links\">\n    <a class=\"time-icons time-icons-mail social-link-mail\" href=\"mailto:?subject=Priests%20Assaulted%20in%20Guinea%20After%20Being%20Mistaken%20for%20Ebola%20Workers%20%7C%20TIME&body=Priests%20Assaulted%20in%20Guinea%20After%20Being%20Mistaken%20for%20Ebola%20Workers%0A%0AThey%20had%20gone%20to%20a%20local%20village%20to%20spray%20insecticides%0A%0Ahttp%3A%2F%2Ftime.com%2F3675775%2Febola-guinea-priests-beaten-village%2F\" data-event=\"email\" title=\"Click to Email this article\"><\/a>\n    <a class=\"time-icons time-icons-fb social-link-fb popup\" href=\"https:\/\/www.facebook.com\/sharer\/sharer.php?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftime.com%2F3675775%2Febola-guinea-priests-beaten-village%2F\" data-event=\"fb-share\" title=\"Click to post this article to Facebook\"><\/a>\n    <a class=\"time-icons time-icons-tw social-link-tw popup\" href=\"#\" data-href=\"https:\/\/twitter.com\/intent\/tweet?url=http%3A%2F%2Fti.me%2F1C72VL3&text=Priests%20assaulted%20in%20Guinea%20after%20being%20mistaken%20for%20Ebola%20workers&via=TIMEHealth\" data-event=\"tweet\" title=\"Click to Tweet this article\"><\/a>\n    <a class=\"time-icons time-icons-linkedin social-link-linkedin popup\" href=\"http:\/\/www.linkedin.com\/shareArticle?mini=true&url=http%3A%2F%2Fti